### Obter todos os ambientes
GET http://localhost:8080/ambiente?pagina=0&tamanho=10

### Obter ambiente por id
GET http://localhost:8080/ambiente/4e2500ad-3537-4ae7-b5b8-58e756e69c0b

### Criar ambiente
POST http://localhost:8080/ambiente
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "nome": "Ambiente 2"
}

### Atualizar ambiente
PUT http://localhost:8080/ambiente/4e2500ad-3537-4ae7-b5b8-58e756e69c0b
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Ambiente NOVO 2"
}

### Deletar ambiente
DELETE http://localhost:8080/ambiente/4e2500ad-3537-4ae7-b5b8-58e756e69c0b
